aVPietro was suspicious of formal art training,
p38
aVart history training, because he feared
p39
aVthat it filled people up with jargon, and then they just
p40
aVclassified things rather than looking at them,
p41
aVand he wanted to remind us that all art was once contemporary,
p42
aVand he wanted us to use our eyes,
